     H            Y.
     F** ADAR48 ****************************************
     F*.. PUBLICSATION OF DATA CHECK LIST WHICH PRODUCTION ORDER AGAIN AND OVER
     F*MADE <1> *
     F*                S.YAMAGMI 92.03.25              *
     F**************************************************
     FADAPW48 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FADAPL05 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
     FADAWP48 O   F      50            DISK
     E                    ER      1   6 60               d[ｰxｮﾈｰﾆﾞ
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80@HIZ
     I                                        1   40@Y
     I                                        5   60@M
     I                                        7   80@D
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80ADKOHZ
     I                                        1   40ADKOYY
     I                                        5   60ADKOMM
     I                                        7   80ADKODD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 ADHIN
     I                                        1   5 ADHIN1
     I                                        6  10 ADHIN2
     I                                       11  12 ADHIN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A2GSHZ
     I                                        1   40A2GSYY
     I                                        5   60A2GSMM
     I                                        7   80A2GSDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80A2TRHZ
     I                                        1   40A2TRYY
     I                                        5   60A2TRMM
     I                                        7   80A2TRDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 A2STK
     I                                        1   1 A2STRK
     I                                        2   3 A2STRT
     I                                        4   5 A2STRR
     I                                        6   6 A2STRD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 A2KTK
     I                                        1   1 A2KTRK
     I                                        2   3 A2KTRT
     I                                        4   5 A2KTRR
     I                                        6   6 A2KTRD
      *
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           PUSER
     C                     KFLD           @Y
     C                     KFLD           @M
     C                     KFLD           @D
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           ADHIN1
     C                     KFLD           ADHIN2
     C                     KFLD           ADHIN3
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PUSER  10
     C                     PARM           PNO     1
     C                     PARM           PHIZ    8
      *
     C           STEP1     TAG
     C                     Z-ADD0         @HIZ
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    @NO
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    WTK     6
     C           STEP2     TAG
     C                     EXFMTADAPW481
     C                     SETOF                     010299
     C                     SETOF                     U1U2
      *
     C           *INKA     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     END
      *
     C           @HIZ      IFEQ 0
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     MOVE ER,1      MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C           @M        IFLT 1
     C           @M        ORGT 12
     C           @D        ORLT 1
     C           @D        ORGT 31
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     MOVE ER,2      MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C           @HIZ      IFGT *DATE
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     MOVE ER,3      MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C           @NO       IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     MOVE ER,4      MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C           @NO       IFNE '1'
     C           @NO       ANDNE'2'
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     MOVE ER,5      MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C           *INKE     IFEQ '0'
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
      *~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
      * mﾞｰj --> WORKFILE(ADAWP48)
      *____________________________
      *
     C           KEY       SETLLADAPL051
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     SETOF                     20
     C           KEY       READEADAPL051                 20
     C           *IN20     IFEQ '1'
     C                     GOTO END
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETOF                     30
     C           KEY1      CHAINFCEPL011             30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '1'
     C           A2GSKD    OREQ 'D'
     C           A2GSHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     GOTO END
     C                     END
      *
     C           @HIZ      IFGE A2TRHZ
     C                     MOVELA2STK     WTK
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVELA2KTK     WTK
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVEL@HIZ      PHIZ
      *
     C                     EXCPTDAT
     C                     MOVE '*'       SW      1
      *
     C           END       TAG
     C  N20                END
      *
     C           SW        IFNE '*'
     C                     SETON                     99
     C                     MOVE ER,6      MSG
     C                     GOTO STEP2
     C                     END
      *
     C           @NO       IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     U1
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     U2
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     OADAWP48 E                DAT
     O                         ADHIN     12
     O                         WTK       18
     O                         ADDTKB    19
     O                         ADMAIS    22
**  MSG (ERROR MESSAGE )
E-01 INPUT HANDLING DATE
E-02 HANDLING DATE ISN'T RIGHT
E-03 HANDLING DATE IS BIG
E-04 APPOINT OUTPUT FORM
E-05 OUTPUT FORM IS 1 OR  2.
E-06 HANDLING DAY OF SCREEN DOESN'T INCLUDE YOUR DATA
